thread.title_full: Auto Europe Australia reviewed by Roger+Starbuck

author: Roger+Starbuck
title: Roger+Starbuck
text: I booked through this company twice last year and had excellent service. Admittedly I was a little nervous at such good rates being charged here and was concerned I might have hidden costs on arrival and pickup. My concerns were totally unfounded.
